column14:
1. As a customer, I am required to add username so that I can login
2. As a customer, I am required to add password so that I can login
3. As a customer, I am required to add full name so that I am recognize by driver and make reservation
4. As a customer, I am required to add contact number so that I can be contacted by driver and staff
5. As a customer, I am required to add email address so that i can receive the latest news and promotion
6. As a customer, I am required to add date of birth so that staff can send me birthday wishes and birthday promotion or voucher.

As a customer, I can make payment with PayPal by entering card type, card number, card security code and expiry date for payment method, and the username and password for login, so that the system will verify the card and the user, and able to make payment.
As a customer, I can delete the payment details according to the payment date so that the oldest payment records can be deleted.
